55
00:07:29,662 --> 00:07:36,627
ZONA DE EXCLUSÃO DE CHERNOBYL

56
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:01,360
Legasov.

57
00:08:03,154 --> 00:08:05,072
Encontro com ele lá.

58
00:09:03,380 --> 00:09:05,925
